DIA_OPEN.text: Hey there  I m ProfessorŇFennel, As you can see  I mŇa scientist,ȼIn fact  the subject I mŇresearching is Trainers ȼMy dream is to collect saveŇfiles of various trainers Ňbut I haven t had anyŇbreakthroughs yet,,,ȼSo in the meantime  I veŇbeen working on a differentŇproject with one of my oldŇfriends ȼIn my home region  there s aŇlocation that can make aŇPok mon s dreams intoŇreality,ȼThis means that any otherŇPok mon they meet in theirŇdreams become real ȼThat s fantastic  but myŇgoal is to do the same  justŇwith a trainer s dreamŇinstead ȼThat s why I need your help ŇI want to bring as manyŇPok mon out of your dreamsŇas possible ȼThere s just over 250ŇPok mon I want to catalogueŇin my Dream Pok Dex  orŇDream Dex for short,ȼBut I ll let you keep anyŇPok mon  they re from yourŇdreams after all ȼOne last note  save dataŇbackups are recommended Ňjust on the off chance thatŇsomething goes wrong ȼI think that s everything,,,Ňwhenever you re ready toŇstart  just let me know ƞ

DIA_E4.text: Hi trainer  I m thrilledŇyou ve decided to help withŇour research  but we needŇthe best of the best ȼCome back after you veŇbeaten the Elite Four andŇbecome the Champion ƞ

DIA_MG_FRLGE.text: Sorry trainer  one moreŇthing to take care of beforeŇwe can begin  you need toŇenable MYSTERY GIFT ȼHead to the nearest Pok ŇMart and fill out theŇquestionnaire as follows:ŇLINK TOGETHER WITH ALL,ȼAfter that  you should beŇall set to go  See you soon ƞ

DIA_MG_RS.text: Sorry trainer  one moreŇthing to take care of beforeŇwe can begin  you need toŇenable MYSTERY EVENT ȼHead to the PETALBURGŇPok mon Center and tell theŇman next to the PC: MYSTERYŇEVENT IS EXCITING,ȼAfter that  you should beŇall set to go  See you soon ƞ

DIA_LETS_START.text: Perfect  that s all theŇinformation I need  Let sŇget started ƞ

DIA_START.text: On a second Game Boy familyŇsystem  please load the GameŇBoy Pok mon game you wish toŇtransfer from,ȼIn your Game Boy Pok monŇgame  make your current boxŇthe one you want to transferŇfrom,ȼThen connect this Game BoyŇAdvance to the other GameŇBoy family system using aŇGame Boy Color link cable,ȼOnce you re ready  press AŇon this device  talk to theŇCable Club attendant  andŇthen initiate a trade,ƞ

DIA_OPEN.text: Hey there! I’m Professor Fennel. AsŇyou can see, I’m a scientist. InŇfact, the subject I’m researching isŇTrainers!ȼMy dream is to collect save files ofŇvarious trainers, but I haven’t hadŇany breakthroughs yet...ȼSo in the meantime, I’ve been workingŇon a different project with one of myŇold friends!ȼIn my home region, there’s a locationŇthat can make a Pokémon’s dreams intoŇreality.ȼThis means that any other PokémonŇthey meet in their dreams becomeŇreal!ȼThat’s fantastic, but my goal is toŇdo the same- just with a trainer’sŇdream instead! DIA_E4.text: Hi trainer! I’m thrilled you’veŇdecided to help with our research,Ňbut we need the best of the best!ȼCome back after you’ve beaten theŇElite Four and become the Champion!ƞ

DIA_LETS_START.text: Perfect, that’s all the information IŇneed! Let’s get started!ƞ

DIA_NEW_DEX.text: It looks like there’s at least oneŇnew Pokémon here that isn’t in theŇDream Dex! I’ll give them somethingŇextra sweet as a reward for you both.ƞ
